      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document discusses point-to-point and multi-endpoint topologies used in environments based on the Real-time Transport Protocol (RTP).  In particular, centralized topologies commonly employed in the video conferencing industry are mapped to the RTP terminology.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
